race.description: Crystalite Linemarking Showcase Super Mdn Hcp
race.comment: RIVER BISCOTTE (3) improving gelding who was hunted out from the sticky barrier when sitting up on the pace for a tenacious third over 1200m at Port Macquarie with the 59kg. Nice weight drop today and maps to get the gun run. Goes close. PARALIA (5) shouldered the 59kg at his second run back when a fading fifth over 1400m at Scone in a solid rating contest. Has the speed to take up a position from the draw and figure prominently. RUSTEMO (1) another from the Kris Lees yard due for a change of luck. Finished runner-up again when a plugging second over 1400m at Scone. Stalks the speed and gets every chance. ARGERICH (8) kept fresh and drops sharply in trip. Went out fast with the 52kg before knocking up in the straight with a poor fifth over 2040m at Doomben. Stays in the calculations.
